地脉周流無息坎不平月水滿而圓水傾而<graphic n="KR0628" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0628.png" mimeType="image/png"/>坎之缺<pc n="lb"/>
