行西時㬈<graphic n="KR2789" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2789.png" mimeType="image/png"/>行南時大<graphic n="KR3424" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR3424.png" mimeType="image/png"/>行北時嚴殺順太陽實元煖<pc n="lb"/>
